title: Vancouver Wayzgoose Photos
content: As posted by the [Alcuin Society](http://web.archive.org/web/20120802075957/http:/www.flickr.com/photos/alcuinsociety/sets/72157603225524485/): there are also some pictures of what Jim Rimmer took with him that we saw at his studio the day before. I've got five of the printer's ornaments, and that spiffy black type specimen.
author: Linda Cunningham
